'''Itching powder''', also referred to as '''itching dust''', was a substance which induced itching after coming in contact with the skin of an individual. It was employed by the [[Shaman/Legends|shamans]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] to ward off potential enemies. The [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]] once used itching powder to ward off a [[glok monster]] when it tried to attack his sweetheart [[Latara/Legends|Latara]] during a trek through the [[glop pits]].<ref name="Night of the Stranger" />

